<h3 id="ç¦»æ•£å‹-1">ç¦»æ•£å‹</h3>
<p>è‹¥ç¦»æ•£å‹éšæœºå˜é‡$X$çš„åˆ†å¸ƒå¾‹ä¸º$P\left{ X = x_{i} \right} = p_{i}$ ï¼Œä¸”çº§æ•°$E(X) = \sum_{i}^{}{x_{i}p_{i} }$ç»å¯¹æ”¶æ•›ï¼Œåˆ™ç§°$E(x)$ä¸ºéšæœºå˜é‡$X$çš„æ•°å­¦æœŸæœ›ã€‚</p>
<h3 id="è¿ç»­å‹-1">è¿ç»­å‹</h3>
<p>$X\sim f(x),E(X) = \int_{- \infty}^{+ \infty}{xf(x)dx}$</p>
<h3 id="æ€§è´¨-4">æ€§è´¨</h3>
<ul>
  <li>$E(C) = C,E\lbrack E(X)\rbrack = E(X)$</li>
  <li>$E(C_{1}X + C_{2}Y) = C_{1}E(X) + C_{2}E(Y)$</li>
  <li>è‹¥$X$å’Œ$Y$ç‹¬ç«‹ï¼Œåˆ™$E(XY) = E(X)E(Y)$</li>
  <li>$\left\lbrack E(XY) \right\rbrack^{2} \leq E(X^{2})E(Y^{2})$</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="éšæœºå˜é‡å‡½æ•°çš„æ•°å­¦æœŸæœ›">éšæœºå˜é‡å‡½æ•°çš„æ•°å­¦æœŸæœ›</h3>
<p>å¯¹äºå‡½æ•°$Y = g(x)$</p>
<h4 id="xä¸ºç¦»æ•£å‹">$X$ä¸ºç¦»æ•£å‹</h4>
<p>$P{ X = x_{i}} = p_{i},E(Y) = \sum_{i}^{}{g(x_{i})p_{i} }$ï¼›</p>
<h4 id="xä¸ºè¿ç»­å‹">$X$ä¸ºè¿ç»­å‹</h4>
<p>$X\sim f(x),E(Y) = \int_{- \infty}^{+ \infty}{g(x)f(x)dx}$
æ‰©å±•åˆ°å¤šç»´å‡½æ•°ï¼š$Z = g(X,Y)$;$\left( X,Y \right)\sim P{ X = x_{i},Y = y_{j}} = p_{ {ij} }$;$E(Z) = \sum_{i}^{}{\sum_{j}^{}{g(x_{i},y_{j})p_{ {ij} } } }$ $\left( X,Y \right)\sim f(x,y)$;$E(Z) = \int_{- \infty}^{+ \infty}{\int_{- \infty}^{+ \infty}{g(x,y)f(x,y)dxdy} }$</p>
<h2 id="æ–¹å·®">æ–¹å·®</h2>
<p>$D(X) = E\left\lbrack X - E(X) \right\rbrack^{2} = E(X^{2}) - \left\lbrack E(X) \right\rbrack^{2}$ï¼Œæœ‰æ—¶ä¹Ÿè®°ä½œ$Var(X)$ã€‚
åŒæ—¶å¼•å…¥æ ‡å‡†å·®ï¼ˆå‡æ–¹å·®ï¼‰$\sigma (x)=\sqrt{D(X)}$ã€‚</p>
<h3 id="ç¦»æ•£å‹-2">ç¦»æ•£å‹</h3>
<p>$D(X) = \sum_{i}^{}{\left\lbrack x_{i} - E(X) \right\rbrack^{2}p_{i} }$</p>
<h3 id="è¿ç»­å‹-2">è¿ç»­å‹</h3>
<p>$D(X) = {\int_{- \infty}^{+ \infty}\left\lbrack x - E(X) \right\rbrack}^{2}f(x)dx$</p>
<h3 id="æ€§è´¨-5">æ€§è´¨</h3>
<ul>
  <li>$\ D(X) = E(X^{2}) - E^{2}(X)$</li>
  <li>$\ D(C) = 0,D\lbrack E(X)\rbrack = 0,D\lbrack D(X)\rbrack = 0$</li>
  <li>$\ D\left( C_{1}X + C_{2} \right) = C_{1}^{2}D\left( X \right)$</li>
  <li>$X$ä¸$Y$ç›¸äº’ç‹¬ç«‹ï¼Œåˆ™$D(X \pm Y) = D(X) + D(Y)$</li>
  <li>$\ D(X) = 0 \Leftrightarrow P\left{ X = C \right} = 1$</li>
  <li>$\ D\left( X \right) &lt; E\left( X - C \right)^{2},C \neq E\left( X \right)$</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="chebyshevåˆ‡æ¯”é›ªå¤«ä¸ç­‰å¼">Chebyshevï¼ˆåˆ‡æ¯”é›ªå¤«ï¼‰ä¸ç­‰å¼</h3>
<p>è‹¥éšæœºå˜é‡$X$æ»¡è¶³$E(X)=\mu$ï¼Œæ–¹å·®$D(x)=\sigma^2$ï¼Œåˆ™å¯¹äºä»»æ„æ­£æ•°$\varepsilon$ï¼Œæœ‰åˆ‡æ¯”é›ªå¤«ä¸ç­‰å¼$P{|X-\mu|\ge\varepsilon}\leq\frac{\sigma^2}{\varepsilon^2}$æˆç«‹ã€‚</p>
<h2 id="åæ–¹å·®åŠç›¸å…³ç³»æ•°">åæ–¹å·®åŠç›¸å…³ç³»æ•°</h2>
<p>$Cov(X,Y) = E\left\lbrack (X - E(X)(Y - E(Y)) \right\rbrack$ç§°ä¸ºéšæœºå˜é‡$X,Y$çš„åæ–¹å·®ï¼Œ$\rho_{ {XY} } = \frac{Cov(X,Y)}{\sqrt{D(X)}\sqrt{D(Y)} }$ç§°ä¸ºä»–ä»¬çš„ç›¸å…³ç³»æ•°ã€‚</p>
<h3 id="æ€§è´¨-6">æ€§è´¨</h3>
<ul>
  <li>$\ Cov(X,Y) = Cov(Y,X)$</li>
  <li>$\ Cov(aX,bY) = abCov(Y,X)$</li>
  <li>$\ Cov(X_{1} + X_{2},Y) = Cov(X_{1},Y) + Cov(X_{2},Y)$</li>
  <li>
    <table>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>$\ \left</td>
          <td>\rho\left( X,Y \right) \right</td>
          <td>\leq 1$</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </li>
  <li>$\ \rho\left( X,Y \right) = 1 \Leftrightarrow P\left( Y = aX + b \right) = 1$ ï¼Œå…¶ä¸­$a &gt; 0$</li>
  <li>$\rho\left( X,Y \right) = - 1 \Leftrightarrow P\left( Y = aX + b \right) = 1$ï¼Œå…¶ä¸­$a &lt; 0$</li>
  <li>ä¸€èˆ¬æœ‰ $D(X \pm Y) = D(X) + D(Y) \pm 2Cov(X,Y) = D(X) + D(Y) \pm 2\rho\sqrt{D(X)}\sqrt{D(Y)}$</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="é‡è¦å…¬å¼ä¸ç»“è®º-1">é‡è¦å…¬å¼ä¸ç»“è®º</h3>
