  <li>$\ Cov(X,Y) = E(XY) - E(X)E(Y)$</li>
  <li>
    <table>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>$\left</td>
          <td>\rho\left( X,Y \right) \right</td>
          <td>\leq 1,$ä¸” $\rho\left( X,Y \right) = 1 \Leftrightarrow P\left( Y = aX + b \right) = 1$ï¼Œå…¶ä¸­$a &gt; 0$</td>
