<h3 id="å¸¸ç”¨ç»Ÿè®¡é‡åˆ†å¸ƒ">å¸¸ç”¨ç»Ÿè®¡é‡åˆ†å¸ƒ</h3>
<h4 id="chi2åˆ†å¸ƒ">$\chi^{2}$åˆ†å¸ƒ</h4>
<p>$\chi^{2} = X_{1}^{2} + X_{2}^{2} + \cdots + X_{n}^{2}\sim\chi^{2}(n)$ï¼Œå…¶ä¸­$X_{1},X_{2}\cdots,X_{n},$ç›¸äº’ç‹¬ç«‹ï¼Œä¸”åŒæœä»$N(0,1)$</p>
<h4 id="tåˆ†å¸ƒ">$t$åˆ†å¸ƒ</h4>
<p>$T = \frac{X}{\sqrt{Y/n} }\sim t(n)$ ï¼Œå…¶ä¸­$X\sim N\left( 0,1 \right),Y\sim\chi^{2}(n),$ä¸”$X$ï¼Œ$Y$ ç›¸äº’ç‹¬ç«‹ã€‚</p>
<h4 id="fåˆ†å¸ƒ">$F$åˆ†å¸ƒ</h4>
<p>$F = \frac{X/n_{1} }{Y/n_{2} }\sim F(n_{1},n_{2})$ï¼Œå…¶ä¸­$X\sim\chi^{2}\left( n_{1} \right),Y\sim\chi^{2}(n_{2}),$ä¸”$X$ï¼Œ$Y$ç›¸äº’ç‹¬ç«‹ã€‚</p>
<h4 id="æ­£æ€æ€»ä½“çš„å¸¸ç”¨æ ·æœ¬åˆ†å¸ƒ">æ­£æ€æ€»ä½“çš„å¸¸ç”¨æ ·æœ¬åˆ†å¸ƒ</h4>
<p>è®¾$X_{1},X_{2}\cdots,X_{n}$ä¸ºæ¥è‡ªæ­£æ€æ€»ä½“$N(\mu,\sigma^{2})$çš„æ ·æœ¬ï¼Œ$\overline{X} = \frac{1}{n}\sum_{i = 1}^{n}X_{i},S^{2} = \frac{1}{n - 1}\sum_{i = 1}^{n}{ {(X_{i} - \overline{X})}^{2} }$ï¼Œåˆ™ï¼š</p>
<ul>
  <li>$\overline{X}\sim N\left( \mu,\frac{\sigma^{2} }{n} \right){\ \ }$æˆ–è€…$\frac{\overline{X} - \mu}{\frac{\sigma}{\sqrt{n} } }\sim N(0,1)$</li>
  <li>$\frac{(n - 1)S^{2} }{\sigma^{2} } = \frac{1}{\sigma^{2} }\sum_{i = 1}^{n}{ {(X_{i} - \overline{X})}^{2}\sim\chi^{2}(n - 1)}$</li>
  <li>$\frac{1}{\sigma^{2} }\sum_{i = 1}^{n}{ {(X_{i} - \mu)}^{2}\sim\chi^{2}(n)}$</li>
  <li>${\ \ }\frac{\overline{X} - \mu}{S/\sqrt{n} }\sim t(n - 1)$</li>
</ul>

<h4 id="é‡è¦å…¬å¼ä¸ç»“è®º-2">é‡è¦å…¬å¼ä¸ç»“è®º</h4>
<ul>
  <li>å¯¹äº$\chi^{2}\sim\chi^{2}(n)$ï¼Œæœ‰$E(\chi^{2}(n)) = n,D(\chi^{2}(n)) = 2n$ï¼›</li>
  <li>å¯¹äº$T\sim t(n)$ï¼Œæœ‰$E(T) = 0,D(T) = \frac{n}{n - 2}(n &gt; 2)$ï¼›</li>
  <li>å¯¹äº$F\sim{\ }F(m,n)$ï¼Œæœ‰ $\frac{1}{F}\sim F(n,m),F_{a/2}(m,n) = \frac{1}{F_{1 - a/2}(n,m)}$ï¼›</li>
  <li>å¯¹äºä»»æ„æ€»ä½“$X$ï¼Œæœ‰ $E(\overline{X}) = E(X),E(S^{2}) = D(X),D(\overline{X}) = \frac{D(X)}{n}$</li>
</ul>

